Q07FEEDBACK: It was a little more difficult to imagine things when you have to focus on a point with your eyes open
Ik vond de verhalen soms een beetje snel vertelt.

Other than troubles with locating the room, it was actually quite a calming experience. I was quite nervous about blinking too often for the measurements, and it was also a little out of nature to keep the eyes open to visualise so I was sometimes distracted from the material of the stories.
To enhance a participant's visualizations of the short stories, I think a more animated voice and tone would be appreciated
